name: Alisha Finn
description: In my case i would say love make the world go round, instead of money, i am a very jovial and fun person with a very cynical look at life, I am a very hardworking woman and i have achieved major success in my life endeavours and i am looking to settle down with a man because love is all that matters, although i was in a relationship couple of years back but it didn’t end well and i don’t want such traumatic experience happen to me again, I am here for something serious and i want people who seek the same thing to communicate with me. cheers
